    <H2>Dungeons &amp; Dragons Online Dungeon Generator
    <HR SIZE=1></H2>
    <P>

    <DIV CLASS="NORMAL">
    <B>Welcome</B> to the online Dungeons &amp; Dragons Dungeon generator!
    This tool allows you to generate random dungeons for the heroes of
    your campaign to explore.  Try it out!
    <P>
    <B>Dungeon Generator News:</B>:
    <UL>
      <LI><B>20 Nov 2000</B>: Windows version released!  Download it <A HREF="/jgb3/dungeon_win.zip">here</A>!
      <LI><B>20 Nov 2000</B>: Source code released!  Download it <A HREF="/jgb3/dungeon_src.zip">here</A>!
      <LI>Wondering where all this is headed?  Check out my <A HREF="http://rover.byu.edu/jgb3/plans.html">Future Plans</A>
          page to see my projected development schedule!
      <LI><B>14 Nov 2000</B>:  Fixed the oft reported bug of some items being WAY over/underpriced.
          Sorry it took so long to fix -- but it's there now.
      <LI>Interested in making a monetary donation, so that I can continue to create and
          improve applications like this one?  Please <A HREF="http://rover.byu.edu/jgb3/donations.html">click here</A>.
    </UL>
    </DIV>

    <P>
